            <title>小度推出 Tiantian Casa ARIA 智能音箱：透明腔体 + Hi-Res 双金标认证，首发 3199 元</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/727/376.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/727/376.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 00:11:38 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D915846" rel="nofollow">伦流挂科</a> 的线索投递！</div>
